"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-lifestyle-fashion-olympic-oakley-shades-sunglasses-summer-trend-2024-b1175654.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lifestyle|Fashion  Sign up for the best picks from our travel, fashion and lifestyle writers.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the summer months crept in, it appeared the bravest pair of sunglasses the majority would risk were those with bright-orange lenses (see,the rise of the Aperol-spritz shades).\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was beforeOlympicfever took hold.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"August has seen us glued to BBC iPlayer to the backdrop of Clare Balding's musings, Instagram feeds full ofJules Bouyer, and, as it happens, pictures-upon-pictures of the countless cycling-shade iterations which have filled Paris.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.954571824406423, \"rank\": 0.042399225049114767, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}, {\"begin\": 711, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clare Balding\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\"}, {\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.641632473235127e-29, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 876, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.603967022853964e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Oakley to Puma, athletes golfing and running, shooting, volleyballing and pole vaulting all appear to have one thing in common: a shining pair of mirrored shades.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\", \"score\": 0.9939072983169904, \"rank\": 0.0061300494288050004, \"text\": \"Oakley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They could have been neon orange, green or hot pink and with iridescent, red or steel silver lenses - but they all shared the ability to lurch off the screen.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ThenPrincess Annedoubled down on her love of the style (complete with, on separate stylish outings, fashion editor approved boat shoes and a Paris 2024 bucket hat) and the glasses seemed game, set, match.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6601119463495104e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But can anyone pull off the sporting hero staple?\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Abroad, colourful-mirror wrap-around shades come two-a-penny on beaches, as salesmen walk about flogging them at \\u20ac10 a pop.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Brits might have remained reserved in their choices (you would sooner see a family kitted out in theirRay Bans Wayfarers, than anything more abrupt), our European counterparts needed no persuasion to lean in.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, they might have been keeping a closer eye on the Spring Summer 2024 fashion month circuit, where a handful of labels put money on the style winning this year's race.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The biggest backer was Acne Studios, who paired the majority of their looks in Paris with silver, Oakley Encounter-silhouette shades.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acne_Studios\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Acne Studios\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acne_Studios\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acne_Studios\"}, {\"begin\": 2061, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.603967022853964e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\", \"score\": 0.9939072983206062, \"rank\": 0.0061300494288050004, \"text\": \"Oakley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In London, it was Skepta who sent out aviators with mirrored lenses for his label MAINS, while New York brand RETROF\\u00caTE offered green tinged cycling shades which gave a sporty edge to their\\u00a0cropped, tux jackets and cargo, sequin slacks.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2119, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999974993443, \"rank\": 1.5819933523056384e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2134, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skepta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skepta\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skepta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skepta\"}, {\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999436113, \"rank\": 5.6535527377426463e-11, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Key to pulling off the Oakley Olympic look (\\u00e0 laPrincess Anne) is not to try and sport-ify your outfit to match.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just embrace the juxtaposition.\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For: Lovers of Alex Yee  For: The Acne look  For: The bold  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 3438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}, {\"begin\": 2620, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.997977285461619, \"rank\": 0.001145823918569266, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbped